<title>bạqdr yạ gẖạly</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr- bạqdr yạ gẖạly yạ rby yswʿ .. wqwfk mʿạyạ fy wạdy ạldmwʿ
 bạqdr wqwfk wsndẗ kfwfk .. wnwrk fy lyly wḍy ạlsẖmwʿ
 bạqdr yạ gẖạly yạ rby yswʿ
 1- dạ kạm mrẗ sẖftk ạ̹lh ạlạ̉mạnẗ .. mạtqdrsẖ tnkr fy nfsk kẖṣạl
 lkn jwh qlby mʿsẖsẖ kẖyạnẗ .. wkạn jwh fkry ṭmwḥy wậmạl
 fḍlt tdạry wsẖry twạry .. mʿ ạ̹ny fy jhly rfḍtk ktyr
 lạ̉nk ḥbyby wḥbk ṭbyby .. mạqltsẖ lqlby hạtrjʿ ksyr
 wjạny klạmk wjạb ly slạmk .. wjyt bạʿtrf lk wbạskb dmwʿ
 bạqdr yạ gẖạly yạ rby yswʿ
 2- ktyr knt bạʿnd wạksr klạmk .. mạbạfrqsẖ ʿn sạỷr ạlmkẖlwqạt
 bạḥkm fy rạ̉yy wạ̉ḍyʿ slạmk .. wạ̉kẖrẗ ạ̹rạdty kẖsạrẗ wậhạt
 bạḥwsẖ lnfsy wạ̉kwm lnfsy .. wmsẖ ʿạrf ạ̹ny bạḥwsẖ nfạyẗ
 wlmạ wṣlt lạ̉kẖry fy yạ̉sy .. ṣrkẖt yạ rby wqlt kfạyẗ
 mạʿdtsẖ ạ̉sybk hạtbt fy ạ̹ydk .. wybqy̱ mkạnk dạ jwh ạlḍlwʿ
 bạqdr yạ gẖạly yạ rby yswʿ
 3- snyny ạlly fạtt msẖythạ mʿạyạ .. btqnʿny ạ̹nk ạ̉mạny ạlwḥyd
 wbhjẗ kẖlạṣk btmlạ smạyạ .. wbtqwl ly ạ̹nk mʿạyạ ạ̉kyd
 btrḥm gẖbạỷy sẖrwdy wfrạqy .. wtrjʿ tfkrny ạ̹nk mʿạyạ
 bḥbk tḥạṣr wạ̹ydk tnạṣr .. wṣwtk yqwl ly ạ̉nạ lyk ḥmạyẗ
 wjyt bạnḥny lk wạ̉qdr jmylk .. wạ̉qwl lk ḥạwṭny lậkẖr ạlrbwʿ
 bạqdr yạ gẖạly yạ rby yswʿ</lyrics>
